# 測試登入 API

### 測試用戶登入 - 成功案例
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "rick",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 測試用戶登入 - 失敗案例（錯誤密碼）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "rick",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 測試用戶登入 - 失敗案例（不存在的用戶）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "nonexistent",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 獲取所有訊息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages?page=0&size=5

### 獲取特定用戶的訊息
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/rick/messages?page=0&size=5

### 創建新訊息
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "rick",
  "content": "這是一則測試訊息！"
}

### 註冊新用戶
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "email": "test@example.com"
}